00:15:30.580 --> 00:15:33.210
Usually I don't let
these names get to me,

00:15:33.210 --> 00:15:35.460
but sometimes it really
affects the way I think.

00:15:35.460 --> 00:15:38.390
I know it's stupid that it gets
to me, but I can't help it.

00:15:38.390 --> 00:15:41.470
Once I was told I was worthless
and I'd never go anywhere in life.

00:15:41.470 --> 00:15:43.090
It really made me think
about suicide.

00:15:43.090 --> 00:15:45.150
I planned to kill myself just

00:15:45.150 --> 00:15:47.250
because some people thought
it'd be delightful to make fun

00:15:47.250 --> 00:15:48.800
of my insecurities relentlessly.

00:15:48.800 --> 00:15:52.960
I realize now that I was just being
crazy for thinking that would work

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:54.260
and would be a good solution,

00:15:54.260 --> 00:15:57.710
but in that moment I really
wanted to end my own life.

00:15:57.710 --> 00:16:01.100
I've learned recently that people
can't hurt me with petty insults

00:16:01.100 --> 00:16:04.800 position:56%
and small stupid assaults anymore,
but if they hurt my friends it feels

00:16:04.800 --> 00:16:07.610
as if something has
shoved a knife into my gut.

00:16:07.610 --> 00:16:09.430
I wanted to write this
paper because I wanted

00:16:09.430 --> 00:16:12.880
to stop seeing good people getting
hurt because of someone else.

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:15.880
I want to see violence removed
from the face of the earth.

00:16:15.880 --> 00:16:18.950
But I believe in something
most people don't,

00:16:18.950 --> 00:16:22.540
violence can't be stopped,
it can be weakened.

00:16:22.540 --> 00:16:24.800
I know that's not the
answer you're looking for,

00:16:24.800 --> 00:16:27.750
but I also know why
it can't be stopped.

00:16:27.750 --> 00:16:29.600
Human psychology is probably one

00:16:29.600 --> 00:16:33.070 position:56%
of the most fascinating things you
could ever learn about in my opinion

00:16:33.070 --> 00:16:36.770
and answers the causes
of violence perfectly.

00:16:36.770 --> 00:16:39.950
Humans are social creatures
with complex thinking processes

00:16:39.950 --> 00:16:44.320
and a wide variety of emotions,
but it doesn't take a genius

00:16:44.320 --> 00:16:47.530
to realize we express some
emotions through violence.

00:16:47.530 --> 00:16:50.770
Humans become angry when they
perceive something as a threat

00:16:50.770 --> 00:16:52.170
to their mental or physical health.

00:16:52.170 --> 00:16:54.630
It's how we've stayed alive,
if you think about it.

00:16:54.630 --> 00:16:58.090
Back in the Ice Age we were forced
to kill seal, commit violent acts

00:16:58.090 --> 00:17:01.270
at a very young age if
we wanted to stay alive.

00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:05.570
Violence can come from history,
genes and all sorts of things,

00:17:05.570 --> 00:17:08.480
but there are also animal
instincts and respect.

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:10.490
We humans forget that
we were also animals,

00:17:10.490 --> 00:17:14.770
not Godly beings among
other less of all species.

00:17:14.770 --> 00:17:18.080
We may fight for territory,
food and other resources

00:17:18.080 --> 00:17:20.810
because even though we're
the most of all species

00:17:20.810 --> 00:17:24.650
on the planet we're still just
animals who strive to survive.

00:17:24.650 --> 00:17:27.380
We also do have some people
who will fight for respect.

00:17:27.380 --> 00:17:30.970
Many children thirst for respect,
and those who don't might pay

00:17:30.970 --> 00:17:33.410
with it with a few punches.

00:17:33.410 --> 00:17:36.050
Now after all those reasons
why we can't solve violence,

00:17:36.050 --> 00:17:39.390
I'd like to present a few ways
we can lower the amount of it.

00:17:39.390 --> 00:17:41.730
We could easily do what people
are doing now with our schools

00:17:41.730 --> 00:17:43.730
and education, but
that'll take generations

00:17:43.730 --> 00:17:45.710
of people before it
comes into effect,

00:17:45.710 --> 00:17:47.820
which we may not have time for.

00:17:47.820 --> 00:17:50.120
I believe that without medicine
we could be more serious

00:17:50.120 --> 00:17:53.090
about teaching why violence is
wrong to the smaller children

00:17:53.090 --> 00:17:55.140
in preschool and kindergarten.

00:17:55.140 --> 00:17:59.360
Children are more impressionable
the younger they are,

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:03.130
which would make teaching
them not to fight much easier

00:18:03.130 --> 00:18:05.290
than teaching someone my age.

00:18:05.290 --> 00:18:08.840
This would, in turn, make it so
the next generation doesn't fight

00:18:08.840 --> 00:18:11.920
as much, but we'll still
have rule breakers and people

00:18:11.920 --> 00:18:16.740 position:56%
with mental illnesses that will beat
down on people or even kill them.

00:18:16.740 --> 00:18:19.620
There is no perfect system to end
physical violence, but there can be

00:18:19.620 --> 00:18:22.290
for mental violence in my opinion.

00:18:22.290 --> 00:18:25.370 position:56%
Most children if they want to insult
someone will do it over the internet

00:18:25.370 --> 00:18:27.740
where a victim cannot
retaliate easily.

00:18:27.740 --> 00:18:32.050
