00:50:03.540 --> 00:50:05.970
to promote what is good in them.

00:50:05.970 --> 00:50:11.030
And so and I think this third
quality is what Sally was talking

00:50:11.030 --> 00:50:17.840
about is that is if we can
see the strength in everyone,

00:50:17.840 --> 00:50:19.210
that everyone has strengths.

00:50:19.210 --> 00:50:21.840
We all have weaknesses,
everyone here has a weakness,

00:50:21.840 --> 00:50:24.100
everyone here has flaws.

00:50:24.100 --> 00:50:29.220
But when we look at an
individual and see their strengths

00:50:29.220 --> 00:50:32.810
and see what is positive
about them and nurture it,

00:50:32.810 --> 00:50:37.380
as opposed to seeing their
problem that we want to fix,

00:50:37.380 --> 00:50:40.230
then we're on our way
towards helping

00:50:40.230 --> 00:50:45.660
